# 📚 EduEire Academic Support App

EduEire is a Flutter application designed to help Irish students easily access **academic support**, **student discounts**, **grants**, **resources**, **motivation**, and **scholarship opportunities** — all in one convenient app.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🧠 **Academic Support**: Tap-to-expand cards inspired by NCI and CareersPortal
- 💸 **Student Deals**: Browse discounted offers for students
- 💰 **Grants & Scholarships**: Learn about financial support options
- 🎯 **Motivational Resources**: Stay on track with curated tips and encouragement
- 📚 **Learning Resources**: Study support and exam tools
- 🔍 **Drawer Navigation**: Quick-access sidebar to switch tabs

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Flutter SDK](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install)
- Dart SDK (bundled with Flutter)
- Firebase CLI (optional if generating config locally)

### 1. Clone the Repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YourUsername/edu-eire-academic-support.git
cd edu-eire-academic-support
